OL,3,CMore parents eligible for certificate
OL,4,Crecognising pregnancy loss
OL,6,FMore parents who have experienced the
OL,7,Floss of a baby early in pregnancy will
OL,8,Fnow be able to apply to have their
OL,9,Fchild's life officially recognised by
OL,10,Fa certificate.
OL,12,FThe government has announced it will
OL,13,Fextend the baby loss certificate
OL,14,Fscheme, which was launched in February
OL,15,Ffor those who have experienced a loss
OL,16,Fsince September 2018.
