OL,3,CMore parents eligible for certificate
OL,4,Crecognising pregnancy loss
OL,6,FThere will now be no time limit on the
OL,7,Finitiative, with certificates
OL,8,Favailable for any parent who has
OL,9,Fexperienced a loss before 24 weeks, or
OL,10,F28 weeks if the loss occurred before
OL,11,FOctober 1992.
OL,13,FAccording to the Department of Health
OL,14,Fand Social Care (DHSC), more than
OL,15,F50,000 documents have been issued
OL,16,Fsince the scheme was launched.
