OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,7,Fthat losing a pregnancy can be "deeply
OL,8,Fdistressing", and added: "There is so
OL,9,Fmuch love and so many dreams for the
OL,10,Ffuture wrapped up in a tiny life".
OL,12,F"That's why it is important for
OL,13,Fbereaved parents to have the option to
OL,14,Fofficially recognise the existence of
OL,15,Ftheir babies and how much they matter.
OL,16,FI'm pleased we can now ensure all
OL,17,Fparents are able to apply for these
OL,18,Fcertificates, no matter how long ago
OL,19,Fthey lost their pregnancies," he said.
