OL,6,FVicki Robinson, chief executive of the
OL,7,Fcharity Miscarriage Association, said
OL,8,Fthe move marks "a significant
OL,9,Fmilestone" for people waiting for this
OL,10,Frecognition.
OL,12,F"For many, even the earliest of losses
OL,13,Fcan be deeply distressing, both
OL,14,Femotionally and physically, but having
OL,15,Fa formal acknowledgement as a marker
OL,16,Fof their loss can be a meaningful part
OL,17,Fof the grieving process.
