OL,3,CMore parents eligible for certificate
OL,4,Crecognising pregnancy loss
OL,6,F"We know from the people that we
OL,7,Fsupport how much the certification
OL,8,Fscheme has helped those who have
OL,9,Fexperienced pregnancy loss, so this is
OL,10,Fgreat news that people whose losses
OL,11,Fwere previously not acknowledged now
OL,12,Fcan be."
OL,14,FThe baby loss certificate scheme was
OL,15,Fformed following the recommendations
OL,16,Fof the independent Pregnancy Loss
OL,17,FReview, which was published in 2023.
