OL,6,FSamantha Collinge, bereavement lead
OL,7,Fmidwife at George Eliot Hospital NHS
OL,8,FTrust and co-chair of the Pregnancy
OL,9,FLoss Review, described the extension
OL,10,Fas a "huge milestone moment".
OL,12,FShe said: "Since I was appointed as a
OL,13,Fbereavement midwife in 1998, I have
OL,14,Fcampaigned for a standardised care
OL,15,Fpathway that ensures that every parent
OL,16,Fexperiencing baby loss ` regardless of
OL,17,Fthe gestation or type of loss `
OL,18,Freceives the physical and emotional
OL,19,Fcare and support they deserve.
